"title": "5589: trap",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5589: trap",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A device used as a snare in hunting or warfare to capture animals or people; a tactic, plot or scheme designed to deceive someone into trouble or sin.</p>\n<h2>Traps used in hunting and warfare</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:24\">JOB 40:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:22\">ISA 42:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:4\">EZK 19:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:5\">AMO 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Kinds of traps</h2>\n<h3>Words</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg12:5-Judg12:6\">JDG 12:5–12:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:2\">PRO 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:13\">PRO 12:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:21\">ISA 29:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:8\">JER 9:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:13\">MRK 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:15\">MRK 12:15</a></p>\n<h3>Actions</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:6-Gen27:12\">GEN 27:6–27:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:23-Gen37:24\">GEN 37:23–37:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:9\">1SA 28:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:5\">2SA 21:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:24\">2KI 21:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:19\">LAM 1:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:9-Hab2:11\">HAB 2:9–2:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:48\">LUK 22:48</a></p>\n<h3>Temptation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9\">1TI 6:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:33\">EXO 23:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:12\">EXO 34:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:16\">DEU 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:25\">DEU 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:12-Josh23:13\">JOS 23:12–23:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:3\">JDG 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:27\">JDG 8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:15-Judg16:16\">JDG 16:15–16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:6\">PRO 11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:25\">PRO 20:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:24-Prov22:25\">PRO 22:24–22:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:26\">ECC 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:18\">EZK 13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:1\">HOS 5:1</a></p>\n<h3>Evil times</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:12\">ECC 9:12</a></p>\n<h3>Fear of other people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:25\">PRO 29:25</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom is alert to traps</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:16-1Chr12:17\">1CH 12:16–12:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:14\">PRO 13:14</a></p>\n<h2>Those who trap others have evil hearts</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:7\">ISA 32:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:3-Ps36:4\">PSA 36:3–36:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:6\">PSA 64:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:14\">PRO 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:20\">PRO 12:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:27-Prov16:30\">PRO 16:27–16:30</a></p>\n<h2>Traps prepared by sinners</h2>\n<h3>Against innocent people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:12\">PSA 38:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8\">GEN 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:21\">2CH 24:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:1-Neh6:4\">NEH 6:1–6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:22\">EST 2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:25\">EST 9:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:11-Job30:12\">JOB 30:11–30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:2\">PSA 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:13\">PSA 31:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:4\">PSA 35:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:110\">PSA 119:110</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:5\">PSA 140:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:3\">PSA 142:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:26\">JER 5:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:8\">JER 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:22\">JER 18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:60-Lam3:61\">LAM 3:60–3:61</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:20\">LAM 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:4-Dan6:7\">DAN 6:4–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:19-Acts23:21\">ACT 23:19–23:21</a></p>\n<h3>Against God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:1-Ps2:2\">PSA 2:1–2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:25\">ACT 4:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:11\">PSA 21:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps83:5\">PSA 83:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:15\">HOS 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:11\">NAM 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Against Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:15\">MAT 22:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:18\">MAT 22:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:15\">MRK 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:21\">MAT 26:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:25\">MAT 26:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:6\">MRK 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:26\">LUK 20:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:6\">JHN 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:3-John18:4\">JHN 18:3–18:4</a></p>\n<h3>Against the truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:8\">HOS 9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:5\">ACT 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:3\">ACT 20:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14\">EPH 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>The wicked caught in their own traps</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:10\">PRO 28:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:10\">EST 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:7-Job18:10\">JOB 18:7–18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:16\">PSA 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:18\">PRO 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:22\">PRO 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:13\">PRO 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:7\">PRO 18:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:6\">PRO 29:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:9\">JER 8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:24\">DAN 6:24</a></p>\n<h2>The devil sets traps</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:7\">1TI 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:10\">ACT 13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:11\">2CO 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11\">EPH 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:26\">2TI 2:26</a></p>\n<h2>God sets traps for the wicked</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:24\">JER 50:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14\">ISA 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:13\">ISA 28:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:9\">JER 8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:43-Jer48:44\">JER 48:43–48:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:13\">EZK 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:20\">EZK 17:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:7\">OBA 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:34\">LUK 21:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:9\">ROM 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:22\">PSA 69:22</a></p>\n<h2>God frees his people from traps</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:3\">PSA 91:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:5-2Sam22:7\">2SA 22:5–22:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:7-Neh4:9\">NEH 4:7–4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:13\">JOB 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:4\">PSA 31:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps124:6-Ps124:8\">PSA 124:6–124:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:9\">PSA 141:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:26\">PRO 3:26</a></p>\n<h3>God forbids the trapping of the innocent</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:17\">ZEC 8:17</a></p>\n<h2>The gospel does not trap people by deception</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:3\">1TH 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:2\">2CO 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:16\">2PE 1:16</a></p>",
